44:56.568 --> 44:58.654
♪ Hell broke luce ♪

45:06.871 --> 45:09.331
Paulie!

45:11.834 --> 45:13.794
Paulie, don't leave me!

45:24.012 --> 45:26.306
♪ Dig damn ditches
In the middle of the road ♪

45:26.390 --> 45:29.518
♪ You pay a hundred dollars
Just for filling in the hole ♪

45:29.601 --> 45:32.354
♪ Listen to the general
Every goddamn word ♪

45:32.438 --> 45:35.315
♪ How many ways
Can you polish up a turd? ♪

45:35.399 --> 45:36.650
♪ And left, right ♪

45:40.237 --> 45:42.906
♪ Left, right
Hell broke luce ♪

45:42.990 --> 45:46.410
Oh, please.
Please, just let me go, man.

45:46.493 --> 45:49.121
Take the money. Take the money, man.

45:49.204 --> 45:50.956
You don't have to kill me over this.

45:51.582 --> 45:54.084
It was him or us!

45:54.168 --> 45:55.669
Oh, God!

45:56.378 --> 45:58.798
- Where did it go down?
- What?

45:58.881 --> 46:01.550
God!

46:02.134 --> 46:03.468
No!

46:04.636 --> 46:07.097
Talk.

46:09.183 --> 46:13.312
Okay! Okay!
It's in the basement of a restaurant.

46:13.395 --> 46:15.689
Linello's in Little Italy.

46:15.772 --> 46:17.858
Okay. I told you. Ow!

46:18.608 --> 46:22.988
No, no, no, no. I told you.

46:23.072 --> 46:24.949
What are you gonna do?

46:25.032 --> 46:26.658
I'm gonna find a home for this.

46:26.741 --> 46:27.993
No!

46:34.708 --> 46:35.750
Help!

47:08.450 --> 47:11.120
No one sleeps
until we get these guys.

47:11.203 --> 47:13.330
Start with this kid, Donald Chavez.

47:13.413 --> 47:15.790
My guy in the precinct called
with an address in Queens.

47:15.875 --> 47:17.626
He lives with his grandmother.

47:17.709 --> 47:20.795
Do what you have to
to make him give up the others.

47:22.506 --> 47:25.217
- Christ. Get the circuit breaker.
- You got it.

47:26.218 --> 47:27.362
Heads up!

48:51.928 --> 48:53.347
Oh.

48:53.430 --> 48:54.431
Oh.

48:56.683 --> 48:59.019
Mmm-hmm...

49:00.020 --> 49:01.480
Yeah, man.

